      "note": "MJPEG starts with JPEG SOI 0xFF 0xD8 — shared with JPEG images. MJPEG raw streams have multiple consecutive JPEG frames (SOI...EOI sequences). In AVI containers, RIFF/AVI magic precedes the frame data; frames use MJPG FourCC."
    }
  },
