  "formatRelationships": {
    "category": "Video",
    "extensions": [".mjpeg", ".mjpg"],
    "relatedFormats": ["JPEG", "AVI", "MOV"],
    "note": "MJPEG has no unique container signature — it starts with JPEG SOI 0xFFD8 shared with still JPEG images. MJPEG is also stored in AVI (RIFF magic, MJPG FourCC) and QuickTime MOV. IP cameras stream MJPEG over HTTP as multipart/x-mixed-replace. Advantage: random access to any frame (no inter-frame dependencies)."
  },
